But what does Xu Huaisong

577
00:40:29,000 --> 00:40:30,440
giving you a New Year's gift mean?

578
00:40:30,800 --> 00:40:33,119
It definitely means something to you.

579
00:40:33,880 --> 00:40:36,159
What? You quit being an editor

580
00:40:36,480 --> 00:40:37,719
and become a love expert?

581
00:40:39,599 --> 00:40:40,480
Even if you are a love expert,

582
00:40:40,480 --> 00:40:42,519
you may not have a good relationship.

583
00:40:43,239 --> 00:40:43,880
But

584
00:40:44,880 --> 00:40:46,239
I, Shen Mingying's best friend,

585
00:40:46,639 --> 00:40:48,039
will never let her miss

586
00:40:48,039 --> 00:40:49,960
her happiness.

587
00:40:51,519 --> 00:40:53,719
His last name is Xu, not Fu.

588
00:40:55,760 --> 00:40:57,920
Fine, I'm a softy.

589
00:40:57,920 --> 00:40:59,000
You are always right.

590
00:40:59,000 --> 00:40:59,679
Fine.

591
00:41:00,320 --> 00:41:01,320
Alright, I'm done talking to you.

592
00:41:01,760 --> 00:41:02,880
I'm covered in sweat from my workout.

593
00:41:02,880 --> 00:41:03,599
I'm going to take a shower.

594
00:41:03,920 --> 00:41:04,440
Okay.

595
00:41:07,079 --> 00:41:08,079
You, the star athlete
of our school's sports meet,

596
00:41:09,400 --> 00:41:10,679
I haven't seen you exercise

597
00:41:10,679 --> 00:41:11,800
since you started working.

598
00:41:12,320 --> 00:41:13,920
Today, the sun is rising in the west.

599
00:41:14,519 --> 00:41:16,559
No, the sun isn't rising in the west.

600
00:41:17,079 --> 00:41:18,519
It's just rising.

601
00:41:20,719 --> 00:41:21,320
I'm hanging up now.

602
00:41:22,079 --> 00:41:22,760
Go.

603
00:41:46,320 --> 00:41:47,639
Lawyer Liu, I saw

604
00:41:47,639 --> 00:41:49,079
the advertisement you posted on your WeChat Moment.

605
00:41:49,079 --> 00:41:50,840
I want to ask you something for my friend.

606
00:41:53,320 --> 00:41:54,400
What do you want to ask?

607
00:41:56,400 --> 00:41:58,440
It's my friend, not me.

608
00:41:59,920 --> 00:42:01,440
Then what does your friend want to ask?

609
00:42:02,719 --> 00:42:03,719
She was cheated on.

610
00:42:04,320 --> 00:42:05,079
Is there any way

611
00:42:05,079 --> 00:42:06,559
to punish her boyfriend?

612
00:42:07,639 --> 00:42:09,599
No, her ex-boyfriend.

613
00:42:11,519 --> 00:42:12,239
Punish?

614
00:42:12,719 --> 00:42:13,840
What do you mean by "punish"?

615
00:42:14,159 --> 00:42:15,559
What exactly are you looking for?

616
00:42:15,719 --> 00:42:16,559
If it's convenient,
we should meet in person.

617
00:42:18,480 --> 00:42:20,199
It's not me,

618
00:42:20,199 --> 00:42:21,239
it's my friend.

619
00:42:24,159 --> 00:42:24,840
Then I suggest

620
00:42:24,840 --> 00:42:26,199
your friend should come

621
00:42:26,360 --> 00:42:27,599
if she has time.

622
00:42:30,199 --> 00:42:31,559
She might not have time,

623
00:42:31,840 --> 00:42:32,880
can I go in her place?

624
00:42:35,000 --> 00:42:35,880
If you know all the details
the details between

625
00:42:36,800 --> 00:42:37,880
your friend and her ex,

626
00:42:38,000 --> 00:42:39,199
then that's fine.

627
00:42:40,519 --> 00:42:41,159
Okay.

628
00:42:53,760 --> 00:42:54,960
Miss Shen, sorry.

629
00:42:54,960 --> 00:42:56,000
Am I late?

630
00:42:56,480 --> 00:42:58,239
No, just in time.

631
00:42:59,000 --> 00:43:00,079
I didn't expect

632
00:43:00,079 --> 00:43:01,719
we'd meet again

633
00:43:01,920 --> 00:43:02,920
so soon.

634
00:43:03,119 --> 00:43:03,639
Yeah.

635
00:43:04,800 --> 00:43:06,400
I didn't really want to see you again.

636
00:43:07,360 --> 00:43:07,960
What are you talking about?

637
00:43:09,039 --> 00:43:09,599
Nothing.

638
00:43:10,159 --> 00:43:11,079
I don't know what you like to drink.

639
00:43:11,079 --> 00:43:12,280
I ordered an Americano. Is that okay?

640
00:43:12,920 --> 00:43:14,159
Sure, thank you.

641
00:43:14,400 --> 00:43:15,280
Excuse me, waiter.

642
00:43:15,280 --> 00:43:16,320
Can I have an orange juice, please?

643
00:43:16,320 --> 00:43:16,880
Okay.

644
00:43:20,079 --> 00:43:20,840
Orange C Americano.

645
00:43:23,119 --> 00:43:24,559
I'm sorry about last time.

646
00:43:24,800 --> 00:43:25,480
It was all a misunderstanding.

647
00:43:26,000 --> 00:43:27,480
I didn't expect a few words

648
00:43:27,480 --> 00:43:29,159
would hit a nerve.

649
00:43:29,159 --> 00:43:29,719
It's fine.

650
00:43:30,000 --> 00:43:30,840
I'm just

651
00:43:31,280 --> 00:43:32,800
perceptive in

652
00:43:32,800 --> 00:43:33,920
useless places.

653
00:43:34,199 --> 00:43:35,000
Right, well,

654
00:43:35,000 --> 00:43:36,239
I'm sorry I mistook you

655
00:43:36,400 --> 00:43:37,719
for a barmaid last time.

656
00:43:39,280 --> 00:43:40,519
Let's get down to business.

657
00:43:41,039 --> 00:43:43,079
Right, when did you...

658
00:43:44,239 --> 00:43:45,320
No, when did your friend

659
00:43:46,000 --> 00:43:46,719
find out

660
00:43:46,719 --> 00:43:47,800
her ex-boyfriend cheated?

661
00:43:48,719 --> 00:43:49,440
Yesterday.

662
00:43:50,400 --> 00:43:51,239
So, do you have

663
00:43:51,239 --> 00:43:52,360
any specific demands?

664
00:43:52,599 --> 00:43:53,519
Like,

665
00:43:53,519 --> 00:43:54,800
reimbursement for expenses during the relationship,

666
00:43:54,800 --> 00:43:56,119
or something extra...

667
00:43:56,119 --> 00:43:57,079
Not financial.

668
00:44:01,000 --> 00:44:02,360
Anything else?

669
00:47:06,519 --> 00:47:07,199
Hello, Dad?

670
00:47:08,519 --> 00:47:08,920
Okay.
I'm heading out now.

671
00:49:00,239 --> 00:49:02,239
Huaishong.
